column5: Looking for a contact for high risk auto insurance, tired of leaving messages and not receiving any calls back.  Tight lines and only big fish ?

Looking  for HIGH RISH insurance usually keeps them away from contacting you. IF you find one it will cost you. just saying. They do know what you have done. Years ago the government used to call it  ‘unsatisfied Judgment’  long gone.
Yep, they'll find you someone that will insure you.
There is an agent/broker in Burlington called High Risk Auto Pro's, that's all the do..
